title: Edit Remote Files via SSH Using Tramp Mode in Emacs
tags: @zettel _method doomemacs ssh tramp
roam-id: fcfad191-e3d2-41cd-bdc6-5eddb418117b
type: text/markdown

- `SPC f f` to `find-file`
- now type `/ssh:` and a new menu will pop up
- select your target host say `192.168.200.100` and you want to login as `root`
- type `/ssh:root@192.168.200.100`
- it will ask for password
- now browse the file system and edit your files
